---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Design Standards Documentation">
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto prose-invert">
    <h1 class="font-saira font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#D9E8F7]">Design Standards Documentation</h1>
    <p class="font-neuton text-body text-[#D9E8F7]">Welcome to the Design Standards Documentation. Please select a section from the navigation menu to view specific standards.</p>
    
    <h2 class="font-saira font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#D9E8F7]">Getting Started</h2>
    <p class="font-neuton text-body text-[#D9E8F7]">This documentation contains comprehensive design standards for various aspects of electrical distribution systems. The standards are organized into sections for easy reference.</p>
    
    <h2 class="font-saira font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#D9E8F7]">How to Update Standards</h2>
    <p class="font-neuton text-body text-[#D9E8F7]">To update the standards:</p>
    <ol class="font-neuton text-body text-[#D9E8F7]">
      <li>Navigate to the GitHub repository</li>
      <li>Find the relevant markdown file in the <code class="bg-gray-800">src/content/sections</code> directory</li>
      <li>Edit the file directly on GitHub or create a pull request with your changes</li>
      <li>Once approved, the changes will be automatically deployed to this site</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</Layout>